# blog-drafts/

This directory contains draft blog posts and articles documenting Intent features, releases, and project updates. Drafts are works-in-progress that may be deferred, revised, or published after dependent work (e.g., subagent dogfood runs) completes.

## Files

- `shell-critic-inception.md` -- Dogfood journal and narrative for critic-shell WP12; documents rule authorship from corpus, dialect handling via shebang detection, and inception-pattern validation
